ity#cite_ref-12" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-12" class="mw-reference-text">Kelly, Anthony, "With Head, Heart and Hand: Dimensions of Community Building" (Boolarong Press) <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt44" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"ISBN","href":"./Template:ISBN"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"978-0-86439-076-9"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwAUA"/><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number" about="#mwt44" id="mwAUE">ISBN</a><span typeof="mw:Entity" about="#mwt44" id="mwAUI"> </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Special:BookSources/978-0-86439-076-9" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-86439-076-9" about="#mwt44" id="mwAUM">978-0-86439-076-9</a></span></li><li about="#cite_note-13" id="cite_note-13"><a href="./Community#cite_ref-13" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-13" class="mw-reference-text"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://cdj.oxfordjournals.org/" id="mwAUQ">Community Development Journal</a>, Oxford University Press</span></li><li about="#cite_note-14" id="cite_note-14"><a href="./Community#cite_ref-14" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-14" class="mw-reference-text">ABCD Institute, in cooperation with the W.K. Kellogg Foundation. 2006. <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.northwestern.edu/ipr/abcd/kelloggabcd.htmll" id="mwAUU"><i id="mwAUY">Discovering Community Power: A Guide to Mobilizing Local Assets and Your Organization's Capacity</i></a>.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-15" id="cite_note-15"><a href="./Community#cite_ref-15" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_n